      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nordstrom-macys-deals-could-put-private-ownership-back-vogue-us-retailers-2024-03-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的上市百货连锁店可能会被私募股权或对冲基金收购，从而极大地改变美国的零售业格局。]]></description>
